text: David Christian Farnsworth (born July 16, 1951) is an American politician. He is a member of the Arizona State Senate and was a member of the Arizona House of Representatives. https://www.azleg.gov/senate- member/?legislature=53&legislator;=1789 ==References== Category:Living people Category:1951 births Category:Members of the Arizona Legislature Category:Politicians from Arizona Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
